OL,3,CWatchdog reverses ruling that Calvin
OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FThe advertising watchdog has reversed
OL,7,Fits ruling that a Calvin Klein poster
OL,8,Fpresented British musician FKA twigs
OL,9,Fas a "stereotypical sexual object".
OL,11,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,12,F(ASA) said it had decided to revisit
OL,13,Fits original decision in January that
OL,14,Fthe poster was likely to cause serious
OL,15,Fharm or offence by objectifying FKA
OL,16,Ftwigs "out of concern that our
OL,17,Frationale for banning the ad was
OL,18,Fsubstantially flawed".
