OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FThe poster featured the artist wearing
OL,7,Fa denim shirt that was drawn halfway
OL,8,Faround her body, leaving the side of
OL,9,Fher buttocks and half of one breast
OL,10,Fexposed, with text reading: "Calvins
OL,11,For nothing."
OL,13,FThe ASA received two complaints that
OL,14,Fthe images were "overly sexualised",
OL,15,Foffensive and irresponsible because
OL,16,Fthey objectified women and were
OL,17,Finappropriately displayed.
