OL,3,CWatchdog reverses ruling that Calvin
OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FFollowing the ruling, FKA twigs, whose
OL,7,Freal name is Tahliah Debrett Barnett,
OL,8,Fchallenged the complaints in an
OL,9,FInstagram post and thanked Calvin
OL,10,FKlein for giving her the "space to
OL,11,Fexpress myself exactly how I wanted
OL,12,Fto".
OL,14,FAlongside a picture of the poster, she
OL,15,Fwrote: "I do not see the
OL,16,F'stereotypical sexual object' that
OL,17,Fthey have labelled me.
