OL,6,F"I see a beautiful strong woman of
OL,7,Fcolour whose incredible body has
OL,8,Fovercome more pain than you can
OL,9,Fimagine."
OL,11,FCalvin Klein also defended the ad,
OL,12,Fdescribing FKA twigs as a "confident
OL,13,Fand empowered woman" who had
OL,14,Fcollaborated with the brand to produce
OL,15,Fthe image and approved it before
OL,16,Fpublication.
