OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FAnnouncing it had reviewed and changed
OL,7,Fits decision, the ASA said: "In our
OL,8,Fprevious ruling we judged that,
OL,9,Fbecause the ad used nudity and centred
OL,10,Fon her physical features rather than
OL,11,Fthe clothing she was wearing, it
OL,12,Fpresented FKA twigs as a stereotypical
OL,13,Fsexual object.
