OL,6,FThe ASA did not ban two posters from
OL,7,Fthe same campaign featuring model
OL,8,FKendall Jenner following complaints on
OL,9,Fthe same grounds, finding that they
OL,10,Fdid not focus on her body in a manner
OL,11,Fthat portrayed her as a sexual object
OL,12,Fand the level of nudity was not beyond
OL,13,Fthat which people would expect for a
OL,14,Flingerie ad.
