OL,3,CWatchdog reverses ruling that Calvin
OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FFollowing the original ruling, the
OL,7,FASA's director of complaints and
OL,8,Finvestigations, Miles Lockwood, said
OL,9,Fthe watchdog found itself "damned if
OL,10,Fwe do, damned if we don't" in such
OL,11,Fsituations, saying: "This is a
OL,12,Fclunking great big poster on the
OL,13,Fstreet in an untargeted medium.
OL,14,FChildren are seeing it alongside
OL,15,Fadults, and sometimes that gets
OL,16,Fmissed."
