OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FMr Lockwood said the decision to ban
OL,7,Fthe ad was made by the ASA's council
OL,8,Fof 12 members, "two-thirds who are not
OL,9,Ffrom an advertising background, and a
OL,10,Frange of genders, ages, backgrounds
OL,11,Fand ethnicities".
OL,13,FHe told PA in January: "Inevitably
OL,14,Fwith this sort of judgment, they are
OL,15,Fsubjective at the end of the day, and
OL,16,Fwe have to make a decision.
