OL,6,F"We are balancing the right of the
OL,7,Fadvertiser's freedom of expression
OL,8,Fwith protecting the public from
OL,9,Foffence and harm, and that's the
OL,10,Fprocess we go through every week."
OL,12,FFKA twigs and Calvin Klein have been
OL,13,Fapproached for comment.
